name: Json
description: Serializes and deserializes primitive and struct values from and to json strings. Supports float, int, string, bool, Vector3, Quaternion, Color, Dict, and List. Dict and List must contain only the supported types, and can be nested.

staticMethods.label: LoadFromString
staticMethods.description: Loads a json string into a custom logic object.

staticMethods.label: SaveToString
staticMethods.description: Saves a custom logic object into a json string.
